[http://www.foldr.org/~michaelw/emacs/mwe-log-commands.el mwe-log-commands]
by MichaelWeber can be used to demo Emacs to an audience.  When
activated, keystrokes get logged into a designated buffer, along
with the command bound to them.

It is not yet a MinorMode, but maybe it will be some day.

